---
title: Pomegranate Pork Steak & Israeli Couscous with Roasted Veggies & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? This pomegranate-glazed pork is sure to pull through for you on hump day with a burst of fruitiness to balance out a tender cut of pork. Make it extra nourishing with a bed of Israeli couscous to have you galloping into the weekend.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pomegranate-pork-steak-israeli-couscous-85432f53.jpg
